 It uses vector graphics to allow for sharp printouts and renderings at unlimited resolution and is not bound to a fixed number of pixels like raster graphics. Inkscape uses the standardised SVG file format as its main format, which is supported by many other applications including web browsers.

 Inkscape supports many advanced SVG features (markers, clones, alpha blending, etc.) and great care is taken in designing a streamlined interface. It is very easy to edit nodes, perform complex path operations, trace bitmaps and much more. We also aim to maintain a thriving user and developer community by using open, community-oriented development.kscreenshotsxphttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/inkscape/Inkscape/21e92689231a3254414f25a728404a8e/screenshots/image-1_orig.pnggversionc1.4ldownload_urlxYoci://ghcr.io/pkgforge/pkgcache/inkscape/runimage/alpine/stable/inkscape:1.4-x86_64-linuxdsizee76 MBjbuild_datet2025-02-02T14:37:39Zhsrc_urlsxMhttps://gitlab.alpinelinux.org/alpine/aports/-/tree/master/community/inkscapehweb_urlsthttps://inkscape.orglbuild_scriptx\https://github.com/pkgforge/soarpkgs/blob/main/packages/inkscape/runimage.alpine.stable.yamlibuild_logxhttps://api.ghcr.pkgforge.dev/pkgforge/pkgcache/inkscape/runimage/alpine/stable/inkscape?tag=1.4-x86_64-linux&download=inkscape.logjcategorieshGraphicsglicensegGPL-2.0kmaintainersx*Azathothas (https://github.com/Azathothas)enotesxRBuilt Using RunImage [alpine]. Check/Report @ https://github.com/VHSgunzo/runimagex@Learn more @ https://docs.pkgforge.dev/formats/packages/runimagex[PORTABLE] (Works on AnyLinux)drankÍ°cpkgqkdenlive.runimagehpkg_namehkdenlivefpkg_idxrunimage.alpine.kdenlivefapp_idporg.kde.kdenlivediconxhttps://api.ghcr.pkgforge.dev/pkgforge/pkgcache/kdenlive/runimage/alpine/stable/kdenlive?tag=25.04.0-x86_64-linux&download=kdenlive.pngkdescriptionx<FOSS video editor, based on MLT Framework and KDE Frameworksgversiong25.04.0ldownload_urlx]oci://ghcr.io/pkgforge/pkgcache/kdenlive/runimage/alpine/stable/kdenlive:25.04.0-x86_64-linuxdsizef225 MBjbuild_datet2025-04-25T19:15:36Zhsrc_urlsxMhttps://gitlab.alpinelinux.org/alpine/aports/-/tree/master/community/kdenlivehweb_urlsxhttps://apps.kde.org/kdenlivex*https://invent.kde.org/multimedia/kdenlivelbuild_scriptx\https://github.com/pkgforge/soarp