kscreenshotsxmhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/io/gpt4all/gpt4all/d22208b160dc858bb78a9516a4835fe1/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxmhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/io/gpt4all/gpt4all/d22208b160dc858bb78a9516a4835fe1/screenshots/image-2_orig.pnggversionr3.3.0.r22.g767189dldownload_urlxdoci://ghcr.io/pkgforge/pkgcache/gpt4all/runimage/cachyos/git/gpt4all:3.3.0.r22.g767189d-x86_64-linuxdsizef639 MBjbuild_datet2025-02-02T14:40:01Zhsrc_urlsx3https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/gpt4all-chat-githweb_urlsxhttps://nomic.ai/gpt4allx#https://github.com/nomic-ai/gpt4alllbuild_scriptxYhttps://github.com/pkgforge/soarpkgs/blob/main/packages/gpt4all/runimage.cachyos.git.yamlibuild_logxhttps://api.ghcr.pkgforge.dev/pkgforge/pkgcache/gpt4all/runimage/cachyos/git/gpt4all?tag=3.3.0.r22.g767189d-x86_64-linux&download=gpt4all.logjcategoriesnUtility,OfficeglicensecMITkmaintainersx*Azathothas (https://github.com/Azathothas)enotesxSBuilt Using RunImage [cachyos]. Check/Report @ https://github.com/VHSgunzo/runimagex@Learn more @ https://docs.pkgforge.dev/formats/packages/runimagex[PORTABLE] (Works on AnyLinux)drankÑcpkgogzdoom.runimagehpkg_namefgzdoomfpkg_idwrunimage.cachyos.gzdoomfapp_idporg.zdoom.GZDoomdiconxqhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/zdoom/GZDoom/91423eede70dce37cec3ab37cdc7906b/icons/128x128/org.zdoom.GZDoom.pngkdescriptionx.Feature centric port for all Doom engine gamespdescription_longy»GZDoom is a source port for the modern era, supporting current hardware and operating systems and sporting a vast array of user options. Make Doom your own again! 

 In addition to Doom, GZDoom supports Heretic, Hexen, Strife, Chex Quest, and fan-created games like Harmony and Hacx. Meet the entire idTech 1 family! 

 Experience mind-bending user-created mods, made possible by ZDoom's advanced mapping features and the new ZScript language. Or make a mod of your own! 

 
Can play all Doom engine games, including Ultimate Doom, Doom II, Heretic, Hexen, Strife, and more 
Supports all the editing features of Hexen. (ACS, hubs, new map format, etc.) 
Supports most of the Boom editing features 
Features complete translations of Doom, Heretic, Hexen, Strife and other games into over ten different languages with Unicode support for Latin, Cyrillic, and Hangul so far 
All Doom limits are gone 
Several softsynths for MUS and MIDI playback, including an OPL softsynth for an authentic ãoldschoolã flavor 
High resolutions 
Quake-style console and key bindings 
Crosshairs 
Free look (look up/down) 
Jumping, crouching, swimming, and flying 
Up to 8 player network games using UDP/IP, including team-based gameplay 
Support for the Bloodbath announcer from the classic Monolith game Blood 
Walk over/under monsters and other things 
 

 Commercial data files are required to run the supported games. For more info about all supported games and their data files, see: Help -> List of supported games. 

 With Flatpak, all file-access is restricted to ~/.var/app/org.zdoom.GZDoom/.config/gzdoom for privacy reasons. You'll have to manually place your IWADs and PWADS there, or you should use an application like Flatseal to give GZDoom additional permissions. kscreenshotsxkhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/zdoom/GZDoom/91423eede70dce37cec3ab37cdc7906b/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxkhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/zdoom/GZDoom/91423eede70dce37cec3ab37cdc7906b/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxkhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/zdoom/GZDoom/91423eede70dce37cec3ab37cdc7906b/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngxkhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/zdoom/GZDoom/91423eede70dce37cec3ab37cdc7906b/screenshots/image-4_orig.pnggversionf4.14.2ldownload_urlxYoci://ghcr.io/pkgforge/pkgcache/gzdoom/runimage/cachyos/stable/gzdoom:4.14.2-x86_64-linuxdsizef349 MBjbuild_datet2025-05-06T19:13:37Zhsrc_urlsx)https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/gzdoomhweb_urlsrhttps://zdoom.org/whttps://zdoom.org/wiki/xhttps://github.com/ZDoom/gzdoomlbuild_scriptx[https://github.com/pkgforge/soarpkgs/blob/main/packages/gzdoom/runimage.cachyos.stable.yamlibuild_logxhttps://api.ghcr.pkgforge.dev/pkgforge/pkgcache/gzdoom/runimage/cachyos/stable/gzdoom?tag=4.14.2-x86_64-linux&download=gzdoom.logjcategorieslGame,ShooterisnapshotsÂfcommits4.14.0-x86_64-linuxgversionf4.14.0Âfcommits4.14.1-x86_64-linuxgversionf4.14.1glicensegGPL-3.0kmaintainersx*Azathothas (https://github.com/Azathothas)enotesxSBuilt Using RunImage [cachyos]. Check/Report @ https://github.com/VHSgunzo/runimagex@Learn more @ https://docs.pkgforge.dev/formats/packages/runimagex[PORTABLE] (Works on AnyLinux)drankwÑcpkgqhaguichi.runimagehpkg_namehhaguichifpkg_idxrunimage.cachyos.haguichifapp_idxcom.github.ztefn.haguichidiconxhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/com/github/ztefn.haguichi/d4793f0a6b4d65d02f0af25dc31261df/icons/128x128/com.github.ztefn.haguichi.pngkdescriptionxGraphical frontend for Hamachipdescription_longy¶Haguichi makes it a breeze to join, create and administer Hamachi networks.

