 This application lets you run Flash content on your computer without a browser in-between, and take full advantage of your GPU and system resources to get those extra frames when playing intense games. 

 Ruffle is an entirely open source project maintained by volunteers. We're all passionate about the preservation of internet history, and we were drawn to working on this project to help preserve the many websites and plethora of content that will no longer be accessible when users can no longer run the official Flash Player. If you would like to help support this project, we welcome all contributions of any kind ã even if it's just playing some old games and seeing how well they run. kscreenshotsxkhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/rs/ruffle/Ruffle/8d54ebabbb33645c790d2510c0269dee/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxkhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/rs/ruffle/Ruffle/8d54ebabbb33645c790d2510c0269dee/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxkhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/rs/ruffle/Ruffle/8d54ebabbb33645c790d2510c0269dee/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngxkhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/rs/ruffle/Ruffle/8d54ebabbb33645c790d2510c0269dee/screenshots/image-4_orig.pnggversione0.1.0ldownload_urlxYoci://ghcr.io/pkgforge/pkgcache/ruffle/runimage/cachyos/nightly/ruffle:0.1.0-x86_64-linuxdsizef232 MBjbuild_datet2025-02-08T11:24:54Zhsrc_urlsx#https://github.com/ruffle-rs/rufflehweb_urlsqhttps://ruffle.rsx#https://github.com/ruffle-rs/rufflelbuild_scriptx\https://github.com/pkgforge/soarpkgs/blob/main/packages/ruffle/runimage.cachyos.nightly.yamlibuild_logxhttps://api.ghcr.pkgforge.dev/pkgforge/pkgcache/ruffle/runimage/cachyos/nightly/ruffle?tag=0.1.0-x86_64-linux&download=ruffle.logjcategoriesx5AudioVideo,Player,Graphics,Viewer,VectorGraphics,GameisnapshotsÂfcommitx(0.1.0___channel____date__-_-x86_64-linuxgversionx0.1.0+$_channel+${_date//-}glicensecMITkmaintainersx*Azathothas (https://github.com/Azathothas)enotesxSBuilt Using RunImage [cachyos]. Check/Report @ https://github.com/VHSgunzo/runimagex@Learn more @ https://docs.pkgforge.dev/formats/packages/runimagex[PORTABLE] (Works on AnyLinux)drankÑcpkgpspotube.runimagehpkg_namegspotubefpkg_idxrunimage.cachyos.spotubefapp_idxcom.github.KRTirtho.Spotubediconxhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/com/github/KRTirtho.Spotube/b191c68e87216afc5215e042699a3592/icons/128x128/com.github.KRTirtho.Spotube.pngkdescriptionsFOSS Spotify Clientpdescription_longyROpen source Spotify client that doesn't require Premium nor uses Electron! Available for both desktop & mobile!

 Following are the features that currently spotube offers:

 
Þ¨ No ads, thanks to the use of public & free Spotify and YT Music APIsô¿ 
ã˜ÿ¡ Downloadable tracks 
ÞËÿ¡ ÞÝ Cross-platform support 
ÞˆÑ Small size & less data usage 
Þçÿ¡ Anonymous/guest login 
Þ Time synced lyrics 
ã No telemetry, diagnostics or user data collection 
Þ Native performance 
